---
title: Spiced Pork Schnitzels with Creamy Potato-Broccoli Toss
description: Easy crumbed schnitzels packed with smokey flavour are the stars of dinner tonight. For the side, our classic potato salad is paired with a crisp leafy salad to round out the meal in a fabulous fashion.
